trans-unit.source: Exception occurs in the case when column set contains duplicated column names and it is not allowed.
trans-unit.target: Exception occurs in the case when column set contains duplicated column names and it is not allowed.

trans-unit.source: This exception occurs when column names are duplicated; that is, not unique.
trans-unit.target: This exception occurs when column names are duplicated; that is, not unique.

trans-unit.source: If any columns have same name, add an instance of <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> between the input dataset and the module raising the error.
trans-unit.target: If any columns have same name, add an instance of <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> between the input dataset and the module raising the error.

trans-unit.source: Use the Column Selector in <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> to select columns to rename, and type the new columns names into the <ui>New column names</ui> textbox.
trans-unit.target: Use the Column Selector in <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> to select columns to rename, and type the new columns names into the <ui>New column names</ui> textbox.

trans-unit.source: If you are renaming multiple columns, ensure that the values you type in the <ui>New column names</ui> are unique.
trans-unit.target: If you are renaming multiple columns, ensure that the values you type in the <ui>New column names</ui> are unique.

trans-unit.source: Column set contains duplicated column name(s).
trans-unit.target: Column set contains duplicated column name(s).
